{"tid":85140,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PS4]  仁王Nioh最後deno 48小時限定","createTime":"2017-01-18T05:59:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-22T09:41:52.000Z","uid":53259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"be5289907396598a5b922b31b5ff45cb7d1e101d","tid":85140,"uid":53259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T05:59:14.000Z","msg":"光榮特庫摩今日正式宣布了動作游戲新作《仁王》將於日本時間 1 月 21 日 0 點正式推送最終體驗版的消息。<br />\n<br />\n本次的試玩版從 1 月 20 日起將可以從 PlayStation Store 中進行預載，解鎖游戲時間為日本時間 1 月 21 日 0 點到 1 月 22 日 23 點 59 分為止。<br />\n<br />\n游玩《仁王 最終體驗版》並通過二俁關卡&ldquo;彼岸的思念&rdquo;的玩家，將可以在正式版中獲得&ldquo;鬼女之面&rdquo;與&ldquo;鬼女之面的制作書&rdquo;兩個贈品。<br />\n<br />\n並且以前通關過 &alpha; 體驗版與 &beta; 體驗版的玩家還可以得到&ldquo;制霸之證：怨靈鬼盔&rdquo;與&ldquo;強者之證：飛緣魔盔&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n《仁王》登陸平台為 PS4，將於 2 月 7 日在北美率先發售，歐洲為 2 月 8 日，日本 2 月 9 日。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.gamecity.ne.jp/nioh/final_demo.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamecity.ne.jp%2Fnioh%2Ffinal_demo.html&d=MCz2kgrv25DYtuinWPPTIksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=48f67a8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gamecity.ne.jp/nioh/final_demo.html</a>"},{"pid":"7f72622ae245c95e060bd8aa55aed3767f4afea6","tid":85140,"uid":53259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T05:59:56.000Z","msg":"Source: <a href=\"https://www.gamecity.ne.jp/nioh/final_demo.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamecity.ne.jp%2Fnioh%2Ffinal_demo.html&d=MCz2kgrv25DYtuinWPPTIksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=48f67a8f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gamecity.ne.jp/nioh/final_demo.html</a><br />\n<br />\n正, 等得好撚辛苦<br />\n要通宵打止一止渴"},{"pid":"d88b4c3c647ca52052c139dbb7a86299a8bd88c8","tid":85140,"uid":53259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T06:12:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"221c14158d51771eaaa27f26033113bcca6986ef","tid":85140,"uid":53259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci